property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey...Did you feel a disturbance earlier?... Meh could just be me..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey, can I bum off some zenny off ya?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I remember myself being deleted.... How am I alive?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I hate going the wrong way...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: There used to be more of us. A green customized Heel Navi was with us all the time till he started acting weird... Then he just cut communication from us all togther... Hope he's alright...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Welcome to the UnderClub! This is our hang out spot since not many go this far actually...What do we do? We just chat, play games, and make stupid bets every Saturday. We don't bother being rude all the time. Gets tiring; just like being nice all the time can also be tiring ya know?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey kid, heard about the rumors? Bunches of BugFrags are popping up randomly... weird right?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Legends say there's this Crazed Navi who's name starts with Bug or something...Powerful too; so powerful he sorta spawned this area we're standing in right now!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I found this cute Moloko all by itself! Decided to adopt it, and saw it already has a name. Wonder who they belonged too...It speaks sometimes, but no one believes me!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I heard from some guy; that somehow they brought this area back from extinction! This place was orignally erased by a powerful Navi... And, now it's back from an assumed powerful Navi... Gee maybe I should be a powerful Navi too huh?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I'm supposed to be deleted.. This land was supposed to be gone. But it's back as if it never happened... And something powerful came with it. Something deep and dark...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: How did you get here? Are you a fan of Team COD?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Then scram! We hate freaking CODs! It's a stupid name, and a stupid team! Go Team Buster!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Good, that team sucks. We root for Team Buster! Everyone knows Busters are the best weapon to have on you no matter what! It never lets you down!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What? Speak up! I don't speak upper people!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: It's weird... From what I learned about this place; this was the ORIGINAL Undernet1. But, it was put into stasis or destroyed or whatever right? So how'd it come back? It's like someone wanted it to come back. I can't imagine someone from the inside breaking free if it was stasis... But, if it was deleted...how does one come back from the brink of deletion? Something doesn't make sense ya know?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: All these BugFrags started showin up. I can finally afford that LifeAura!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Where the hell are these BugFrags coming from? Meh, Whatever.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What's going on with this place?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I need more fire chips to show that I like fire. I should hunt for some Spikey viruses...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Yo, got a fire chip you can trade me? I'm tryna be my own cool hero protaganist who only uses fire chips! I'll call myself the Burning Ronin Navi!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: What if you can spell sus without the sus?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Welcome to the Fire Navi Club! We aim to spread far, and wide! And grow while we're at it! If you can't take the heat then get out!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: So you see me? So I'm not a ghost or something weird...? I'm alive again... What happened to me? I could've sworn I.....

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Bow to Lord Fleetway! He will show us the way! Lord Fleetway is the strongest! Not even BugRiser stands a chance!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Are you also a follower? Of Lord Fleetway?! Our almighty Lord Fleetway is the strongest! He has returned! If you don't want to perish then join us in serving the rightful ruler of the undernet!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: No point on even trying to cut it down; we don't even have a CybrAxe... But, I guess it's fine where it is...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Wonder what's on the other side?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Dude.... What could those Progs be talking about over there? I'd go in myself, but they got it sealed off... Wonder where the password is for the cubes?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey lil ember; this is the Fire Navi Club! You need the password to get in or you're not gettin in... What's the password? You think I'm dumb enough to...ehh why do I care? It's Salamandar... Look; you guard this box 24/7, and get the "Hey man what's the password?" over, and over again...It gets repetitive, and annoying after a whil. I'm the only one to ever be in this position! I'm startin to think they don't like me........

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Wow, somene else figured out how to get over here eh? Good job kid, but im not sure if you want to go further... You see, from what I herd is that this area was deleted because someone wanted to keep somthing away. Wich this area is linked too.... Somthing sinister is beyond this point and every time I felt brave to want to meet it face to face I just get the chills as if whatever is there... It already see's me before I do... Again, I wouldnt go further If if I was you...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I'm trying to find any rare stuff while this place is new!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I WANNA BE PART OF THEIR CLUB, BUT I DON'T KNOW IF THEY WILL ACCEPT ME..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Dude, this place is huge! I could start a hang out here!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE I'M ALIVE BABY! FINALLY I CAN GET BACK AT WHO PUT ME DOWN HERE! THEN IT'S EVERYONES NECKS AFTER!!!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I just came to find rare chips, but what do I find? A lunatic!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Can this clown yell any louder!?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: All the Molokos started eating the BugFrags on the ground. They don't look so good...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Trying to get over there too? Yea I'm trying to figure out the same thing... The password I heard is something...Powerful...Some navi's name... Wonder who's?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Actually I think the password is something else.. Might be something about dying, but for Navis being killed... What was the word...?
